# Go-live checklist maintenance

When you change delivery routing, tracking, dispatch, driver flows, SMS, or pilot readiness:

1. Update [docs/go-live-checklist.md](docs/go-live-checklist.md) in the same session.
2. Set **Last reviewed** to today's date (`YYYY-MM-DD`).
3. Check or uncheck items in Week 1 / Week 2 / Go-no-go tables to match reality.
4. If scope or timeline shifts, update the mermaid Gantt dates or add a short note under **Pilot scope**.
5. If work completes an item tracked on GitHub, mention the issue (#6, #9, #10) in the checklist or board comment.

Do not leave the checklist stale after merging delivery-related features or changing pilot blockers.
